('cb46773a-a3a0-4694-8e2c-185c8a02c438', 'ba1a1cfa-884d-4aad-b2ee-c8a2f458d822', 'd6c8c76c-ffa9-4c03-8985-bbdaf5ff88e7', '12c958f5-3e65-4109-9af0-5606d49005c7', 17, 'When the variable in an equation occurs under a radical, the equation is called a _____ equation.'::text, '[{"key": "A", "text": "Radical"}, {"key": "B", "text": "Absolute value"}, {"key": "C", "text": "Linear"}, {"key": "D", "text": "None of these"}]'::jsonb, 'A', 'extracted', 7),
('f392a269-cd34-4af5-86ce-06143f44cbc9', 'ba1a1cfa-884d-4aad-b2ee-c8a2f458d822', 'd6c8c76c-ffa9-4c03-8985-bbdaf5ff88e7', '12c958f5-3e65-4109-9af0-5606d49005c7', 18, 'x =0 has only ___ solution.'::text, '[{"key": "A", "text": "one"}, {"key": "B", "text": "two"}, {"key": "C", "text": "three"}, {"key": "D", "text": "none of these"}]'::jsonb, 'A', 'extracted', 7),
('3c1b2ff7-00d8-4b1d-989b-c84a4df9764a', 'ba1a1cfa-884d-4aad-b2ee-c8a2f458d822', 'd6c8c76c-ffa9-4c03-8985-bbdaf5ff88e7', '12c958f5-3e65-4109-9af0-5606d49005c7', 19, 'The equation x = 2 is equivalent to:'::text, '[{"key": "A", "text": "x 2or x 2 = =-"}, {"key": "B", "text": "x = -2 or x = -2"}, {"key": "C", "text": "x = 2 or x = 1 2"}, {"key": "D", "text": "x = 2 or x = 1 2 -"}]'::jsonb, 'A', 'extracted', 7),
('b74fa144-872a-4d27-b3ef-c05946a9c5bb', 'ba1a1cfa-884d-4aad-b2ee-c8a2f458d822', 'd6c8c76c-ffa9-4c03-8985-bbdaf5ff88e7', '12c958f5-3e65-4109-9af0-5606d49005c7', 20, 'An __ is equation that is satisfied by every number for which both sides are defined:'::text, '[{"key": "A", "text": "Identity"}, {"key": "B", "text": "Conditional"}, {"key": "C", "text": "Inconsistent"}]'::jsonb, 'A', 'extracted', 7),
('8032a204-d628-4f3c-a72d-cdfb0bbddc93', 'ba1a1cfa-884d-4aad-b2ee-c8a2f458d822', 'd6c8c76c-ffa9-4c03-8985-bbdaf5ff88e7', '12c958f5-3e65-4109-9af0-5606d49005c7', 21, 'An__ equation is an equation whose solution set is the empty set:'::text, '[{"key": "A", "text": "Identity"}, {"key": "B", "text": "Conditional"}, {"key": "C", "text": "Inconsistent"}, {"key": "D", "text": "None"}]'::jsonb, 'C', 'extracted', 7),
('813d2941-ba4c-488d-bb92-d89bb2cc1d13', 'ba1a1cfa-884d-4aad-b2ee-c8a2f458d822', 'd6c8c76c-ffa9-4c03-8985-bbdaf5ff88e7', '12c958f5-3e65-4109-9af0-5606d49005c7', 22, 'A _ equation is an equation that is satisfied by atleast one number but is not an identity:'::text, '[{"key": "A", "text": "Identity"}, {"key": "B", "text": "Conditional"}, {"key": "C", "text": "Inconsistent"}, {"key": "D", "text": "None"}]'::jsonb, 'C', 'extracted', 7),
